# Watson NLC

- training data : https://github.com/watson-developer-cloud/natural-language-classifier-nodejs/blob/master/training/weather_data_train.csv
				  (raw > 복사 > weather.csv 로 저장)

- classify 생성
	1) Natural Language Classifier > 관리 > Access the beta toolkit
	2) Add Classifiers
	3) import training data
	4) create classify

- NLCExample
	NaturalLanguageClassifier service = new NaturalLanguageClassifier();
	service.setUsernameAndPassword("{user id}", "{user pwd}");
	Classification classification = service.classify("{classify id}",str).execute();